The final version that worked for me was:

```
test {
    [...]
    doFirst {
        def testFilter = System.getProperty(&#39;testFilter&#39;)
        if (testFilter) {
            def testFilterParts = testFilter.split(&#39;,&#39;)
            testFilterParts.each {
                item -&gt;
                    filter {
                        includeTestsMatching item
                    }
            }
        }
    }
    [...]
}
```

